snippet.title: WarioWare: Get It Together! - Overview Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Want to see the latest game Wario and friends have been cooking up? Want to learn more about the fast-and-fun microgames? Dive into the details of the WarioWare: Get It Together! game in the video above!

WarioWare: Get It Together! available on 9/10: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/warioware-get-it-together-switch/
